    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_58_3723-3753",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "3723-3753",
      "markText": "大家在阅读本书时，若能时而颔首微笑，时而掩卷沉思，我愿足矣。",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3723&rangeEnd=3753",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=3723&rangeEnd=3753"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_34_1844-1864",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "1844-1864",
      "markText": "说白了，孙悟空自己早就想给唐僧一棍子了。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1844&rangeEnd=1864",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1844&rangeEnd=1864"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_3_934-975",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "934-975",
      "markText": "谁认定的呢？这两位的名声很大：一位是鲁迅，另一位也是鲁迅……哦不对，另一位是胡适。",
      "totalCount": 473,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=934&rangeEnd=975",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=934&rangeEnd=975"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_7_2977-3011",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2977-3011",
      "markText": "这只有一次的生命，到底该怎么使用？这一辈子，到底想成为一个怎样的人？",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2977&rangeEnd=3011",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2977&rangeEnd=3011"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_19_2179-2235",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2179-2235",
      "markText": "狐狸精反映的是男权社会下男人对女人的一种情结，叫恋畏情结——既留恋美女，又怕美女会祸害自己，甚至祸害自己的事业。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2179&rangeEnd=2235",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2179&rangeEnd=2235"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_8_3414-3452",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3414-3452",
      "markText": "这里考考大家，你觉得著名的八仙属于天仙、神仙、地仙、人仙、鬼仙中的哪一类呢？",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3414&rangeEnd=3452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3414&rangeEnd=3452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_13_2892-2919",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "2892-2919",
      "markText": "这说明，少不更事时爱上的人，不一定能给自己带来幸福啊！",
      "totalCount": 357,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2892&rangeEnd=2919",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=2892&rangeEnd=2919"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_42_4136-4212",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "4136-4212",
      "markText": "人参果事件中，镇元子其实没什么损失，还获利巨大。他和孙悟空结拜，还攒局做了主场，治好了身份焦虑。这场疑似故意谋划的风波，对镇元子而言，是一笔划算的买卖。",
      "totalCount": 322,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=4136&rangeEnd=4212",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=4136&rangeEnd=4212"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_14_2268-2297",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2268-2297",
      "markText": "所以，七十二变强于三十六变的说法，完全没有根据，不必相信。",
      "totalCount": 312,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2268&rangeEnd=2297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2268&rangeEnd=2297"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_46_3340-3401",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "3340-3401",
      "markText": "面对不公平的世界，普通人其实还是有自己的解法的：那就是不顾旁人的冷眼，用自己的坚持去做完想做的事，用自己的方式去度过一生。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3340&rangeEnd=3401",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3340&rangeEnd=3401"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_4_3515-3586",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3515-3586",
      "markText": "十世比丘不识真经，齐天大圣难逃掌心。猪面天蓬一路西行，到头来只管坛净。西海白龙做个脚力，卷帘天将指河为姓。不知离了灵台方寸，何处是斜月三星？”",
      "totalCount": 286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3515&rangeEnd=3586",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3515&rangeEnd=3586"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_4_2889-2948",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2889-2948",
      "markText": "佛在灵山莫远求，灵山只在汝心头。人人有个灵山塔，好向灵山塔下修。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2889&rangeEnd=2948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2889&rangeEnd=2948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_26_2702-2723",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "2702-2723",
      "markText": "悟净、悟能、悟空，是有志之士都要走过的路。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=2702&rangeEnd=2723",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=2702&rangeEnd=2723"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_7_2855-2898",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2855-2898",
      "markText": "宋孝宗有句话说得很好：“以佛修心，以道养生，以儒治世则可也，又何惑焉！”（《原道辨》）",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2898",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2898"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_9_2835-2904",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2835-2904",
      "markText": "最后总结一下，成佛有三个标准：自觉、觉他、觉行圆满。这三条，佛都能做到，菩萨能做到前两条，罗汉只能做到第一条。这就是佛、菩萨和罗汉的区别。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2835&rangeEnd=2904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16d32180813ab855bg019d81?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2835&rangeEnd=2904"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300078999_20_1677-1736",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1677-1736",
      "markText": "可能有朋友以为“金秋”这个词的意思是秋天到了，树叶黄了，金灿灿的一片，其实“金秋”的意思是秋天是杀伐的季节，万物肃杀。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300078999&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1677&rangeEnd=1736",
